headline: BD Names Gregory J. Hayes to Board of Directors
summary: BD (Becton, Dickinson and Company) (NYSE: BDX), a leading global medical technology company, today announced the appointment of Gregory J. Hayes to its board of directors, effective March 26, 2025.
